OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson gives insight into
OL,4,Cfarm life and warns of 'catastrophic'
OL,5,Charvest
OL,7,FTV presenter Jeremy Clarkson has
OL,8,Fprovided insight into farming life and
OL,9,Fwarned that this year's harvest "will
OL,10,Fbe catastrophic".
OL,12,FIt comes after the former Top Gear
OL,13,Fstar, 65, said bovine tuberculosis had
OL,14,Fbeen found on his Diddly Squat Farm in
OL,15,FOxfordshire last week.
OL,17,FOn Friday, in a post to X, formerly
OL,18,FTwitter, he said: "It looks like this
OL,19,Fyear's harvest will be catastrophic.
