OL,7,F"That should be a worry for anyone who
OL,8,Feats food.
OL,10,F"If a disaster on this scale had
OL,11,Fbefallen any other industry, there
OL,12,Fwould be a lot of wailing and gnashing
OL,13,Fof teeth."
OL,15,FIn response to a person in the
OL,16,Fcomments section saying that drama
OL,17,Fmakes good TV, he said: "Yes. But most
OL,18,Ffarms don't have TV shows to keep them
OL,19,Fgoing."
