OL,7,FAsked if the farm would be able to
OL,8,Fsurvive without adjacent businesses
OL,9,Flike Clarkson's pub and shop, he said:
OL,10,F"Not a cat in hell's chance."
OL,12,FIn another response, he said: "Normal
OL,13,Fweather would help.
OL,15,F"It never stopped raining in 2024 and
OL,16,Fnever started in 2025."
OL,18,FLast Thursday, he wrote on X that a
OL,19,Fpregnant cow had contracted bovine TB
OL,20,Fon his farm near Chipping Norton.
