OL,7,FCattle which fail a TB test, or
OL,8,Fanimals that have inconclusive results
OL,9,Ffor two consecutive tests, are classed
OL,10,Fas "reactors", and must be isolated
OL,11,Fand slaughtered.
OL,13,FAsked in the comments of his X post
OL,14,Fabout the prize bull called Endgame,
OL,15,Fwhich Clarkson bought recently for
OL,16,F#5,500, he said: "His test was
OL,17,F'inconclusive'.
OL,19,F"I couldn't bear it if we lost him."
