OL,7,FBovine TB is recognised as a problem
OL,8,Fwhich devastates farm businesses and
OL,9,Fis mainly spread through close contact
OL,10,Fwhen cattle breathe in droplets of
OL,11,Fmucus containing Mycobacterium bovis
OL,12,Fbacteria exhaled from an infectious
OL,13,Fanimal.
OL,15,FBadgers can carry the disease and
OL,16,Fculling has long been a part of the
OL,17,FGovernment response to the crisis,
OL,18,Fdespite criticism from wildlife and
OL,19,Fanimal welfare campaigners, such as
OL,20,FQueen guitarist Sir Brian May.
