OL,7,FThe Government said in June it will
OL,8,Fnot be extending the badger cull and
OL,9,Fretains its commitment to end the
OL,10,Fpractice before the next election.
OL,12,FOxfordshire is an "edge area" for
OL,13,Fbovine TB, meaning it is a buffer zone
OL,14,Fbetween high risk and low risk areas,
OL,15,Fso most herds are subject to six-
OL,16,Fmonthly TB tests by default.
