OL,4,Cfarm life and warns of 'catastrophic'
OL,5,Charvest
OL,7,FThe every-day running of Clarkson's
OL,8,Ffarm is documented in a Prime Video
OL,9,Fseries, which first aired in 2021, and
OL,10,Fbrings to light common problems faced
OL,11,Fby British farmers.
OL,13,FClarkson has become a vocal supporter
OL,14,Fof farmers and attended a protest in
OL,15,FLondon against the Government's move
OL,16,Fto introduce inheritance tax on
OL,17,Ffarmland in November 2024.
